@startuml
title 用户注册、登录、修改个人信息时序图

actor 用户 as User
participant ":前端页面" as Frontend
participant ":AuthController" as AC
participant ":UserService" as US
participant ":UserDao" as UD
participant ":DB" as DB

User -> Frontend: 1:填写注册信息，提交
Frontend -> AC: 2:POST /api/auth/register
AC -> US: 3:register(user)
US -> UD: 4:selectByUsername(username)
UD -> DB: 5:SELECT FROM user WHERE username=?
DB --> UD: 6:null
US -> UD: 7:selectByEmail(email)
UD -> DB: 8:SELECT FROM user WHERE email=?
DB --> UD: 9:null
US -> US: 10:BCrypt加密密码
US -> UD: 11:insert(user)
UD -> DB: 12:INSERT INTO user
DB --> UD: 13:1
US --> AC: 14:true
AC --> Frontend: 15:注册成功
Frontend --> User: 16:跳转登录页

User -> Frontend: 17:输入用户名、密码，点击登录
Frontend -> AC: 18:POST /api/auth/login
AC -> US: 19:login(username, password)
US -> UD: 20:selectByUsername(username)
UD -> DB: 21:SELECT * FROM user WHERE username=?
DB --> UD: 22:User
US -> US: 23:BCrypt校验密码

alt 密码错误
    US --> AC: 24:null
    AC --> Frontend: 25:用户名或密码错误
    Frontend --> User: 26:提示错误
else 账号被禁用
    AC --> Frontend: 27:账号已被禁用
    Frontend --> User: 28:提示已禁用
else 登录成功
    AC -> AC: 29:生成JWT Token
    AC --> Frontend: 30:Result{token, userId, username, role}
    Frontend -> Frontend: 31:存储token
    Frontend --> User: 32:跳转首页

    User -> Frontend: 33:修改昵称/头像，提交
    Frontend -> AC: 34:PUT /api/user/profile
    AC -> AC: 35:从Token解析userId
    AC -> US: 36:update(user)
    US -> UD: 37:update(user)
    UD -> DB: 38:UPDATE user SET … WHERE id=?
    DB --> UD: 39:1

    alt 更新失败
        AC --> Frontend: 40:更新失败
        Frontend --> User: 41:提示错误
    else 更新成功
        AC --> Frontend: 42:更新成功
        Frontend --> User: 43:刷新显示新信息
    end
end

@enduml
